{"tid":1385672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［置頂］8.4 東西夾擊大遊行 / 8.5 全民罷工七區集會","createTime":"2019-07-30T06:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T07:00:27.000Z","uid":55257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"71edc318966bee7b49bddeec8058e0dfeb011d87","tid":1385672,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tCLK4sE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtCLK4sE.png&h=d2ec08fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國務院已批出和平遊行集會<br />\n<br />\n呼籲各位8月4日再次上街遊街、8月5日罷工集會，我們再一次重申對特區政府的五大訴求：<br />\n<br />\n一、徹底撤回逃犯條例修訂<br />\n二、收回612暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、成立獨立調查委員會追究警隊濫權<br />\n五、立即實行真正的雙普選<br />\n<br />\n我們熱愛香港，不願再有香港人為守護家園而流血，甚至犠牲寶貴性命。<br />\n<br />\n但我們強調&mdash;&mdash;「沒有暴民，只有暴政」，我們誓必以一切方法迫使政府完全正面回應並實現我們的訴求。<br />\n<br />\n我們促請政府盡快回心轉意，使香港重回正軌，成為團結、民主、自由、公義的社會。<br />\n<br />\n8.4 將軍澳<br />\n13:30<br />\n寶翠公園&mdash;&mdash;&gt;單車館公園<br />\n<br />\n8.4 港島西<br />\n16:00<br />\n科士打臨時遊樂場&mdash;&mdash;&gt;中山紀念公園<br />\n<br />\n8.5 全民罷工七區集會<br />\n13:00<br />\n沙田、荃灣、屯門、黃大仙、大埔、旺角、金鐘<br />\n<br />\n和理非全面上場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b04b35d6d6933adbf62c14639c21c9dd55aa9f","tid":1385672,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:42:10.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"5d52da9393662b7a71363750bdba27fc1cebbc36","tid":1385672,"uid":270276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:42:47.000Z","msg":"【豬腳亮昨晚夢遺報夢】一個戰術<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1384838\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1384838</a>"},{"pid":"b590076ae151d8e5b0217c8d2de4394e1912154a","tid":1385672,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:50:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88c18d2d6729089e67b6d70a653cbcb7a9c52577","tid":1385672,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:00:27.000Z","msg":"光復香港"}]}